{"body": "No, we generally avoid to accept this kind of change because what is a smell to you can not be for others, and we can get another pull request reverting your changes in the future.\r\n\r\nThis is explained here: http://edgeguides.rubyonrails.org/contributing_to_ruby_on_rails.html#write-your-code\r\n\r\n> Changes that are cosmetic in nature and do not add anything substantial to the stability, functionality, or testability of Rails will generally not be accepted.\r\n\r\nDoing this kind of changes when touching in related code is fine.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/9795673", "created_at": "2012-10-25T21:53:46Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/8030#issuecomment-9795673", "updated_at": "2012-10-25T21:53:46Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 8030, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/rafaelfranca", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F2c7b84fa30f0cea96a90729afe2970a0.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/received_events", "gravatar_id": "0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "rafaelfranca", "type": "User", "id": 47848, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237f693bd3543c15100aea7"}, "id": 9795673, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rail